The paper deals with visual question answering, which is a topic in computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as it deals with processing language features. The paper proposes an end-to-end approach that fuses features from multiple local image patches, which is a technique used in deep learning (cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE).
